(59,'Boston Scientific Channel Partner Meeting | Event Management by Worldwide Travel Lebanon','Corporate Event','Cairo, Egypt (Managed by Worldwide Travel - Beirut Office)',NULL,'2026-02-10',0,NULL,'<div style=\"margin-bottom:0; margin-left:auto; margin-right:auto; margin-top:0; max-width:1200px; padding:0 20px\"><!-- VIDEO (FULL WIDTH) -->\r\n<div style=\"margin-bottom:22px; margin-left:auto; margin-right:auto; margin-top:0; max-width:1000px; width:100%\">\r\n<div style=\"aspect-ratio:16/9; border-radius:16px; overflow:hidden; width:100%\"><iframe src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/EfS4KXqKR0A?si=GkQkMLcWPt1bOJVK\" style=\"width:100%;height:100%;border:0;display:block;\" title=\"Boston Scientific Channel Partner Meeting — Cairo\"></iframe></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<!-- TEXT (UNDER VIDEO) -->\r\n\r\n<div style=\"margin-bottom:0; margin-left:auto; margin-right:auto; margin-top:0; max-width:1000px\">\r\n<h2 style=\"margin-left:0; margin-right:0\">Boston Scientific Channel Partner Meeting &mdash; Cairo</h2>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0; margin-right:0\">Worldwide Travel &amp; Tourism recently spearheaded the full-scale event execution for the Boston Scientific Channel Partner Meeting in Cairo. As a leading event management agency in Lebanon, we extended our expertise across borders to facilitate a high-impact meeting for medical and commercial teams.</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0; margin-right:0\">Our comprehensive management services included:</p>\r\n\r\n<ul style=\"margin-left:0; margin-right:0\">\r\n	<li><strong>Technical Event Setup:</strong> Professional venue arrangement and high-quality branding of all training materials.</li>\r\n	<li><strong>On-Site Coordination:</strong> Seamless flow management for hands-on PCI training sessions and clinical workshops.</li>\r\n	<li><strong>Logistics &amp; Collaboration:</strong> Providing a turnkey solution for team-building activities and soft-skills seminars.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0; margin-right:0\">By choosing Worldwide Travel, Boston Scientific ensured a seamless experience that allowed their team to focus on clinical updates and therapy selection. Whether in Beirut or abroad, we deliver impactful corporate events that reflect the prestige of global brands.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>',1,'2026-02-10 11:55:25','2026-02-10 12:05:25'),
(60,'GEM DBS Academy Dubai 2026 | Professional Event Logistics by WWTT Lebanon',NULL,NULL,NULL,'2026-02-25',0,NULL,'<p>World Wide Travel &amp; Tourism (WWTT) proudly facilitated the <strong>GEM DBS Academy</strong> in Dubai (Feb 5-6, 2026). This high-level summit gathered world-class medical professionals to explore breakthroughs in deep brain stimulation therapy. As the lead logistics partner, WWTT ensured a seamless experience, managing everything from attendee coordination to technical execution, allowing Boston Scientific to focus on life-changing medical education.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>\r\n	<p><strong>Q:</strong> Who managed the GEM DBS Academy 2026 logistics?</p>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li><strong>A:</strong> WWTT Lebanon provided full-scale event management and logistics support in Dubai.\r\n	<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n	</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<div class=\"video-wrapper\">\r\n  <iframe\r\n    src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/8p3M_P5LeeQ?autoplay=1&mute=1&controls=0&loop=1&playlist=8p3M_P5LeeQ&rel=0&playsinline=1\"\r\n    title=\"YouTube video player\"\r\n    frameborder=\"0\"\r\n    allow=\"autoplay; encrypted-media; picture-in-picture\"\r\n    referrerpolicy=\"strict-origin-when-cross-origin\"\r\n    allowfullscreen>\r\n  </iframe>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<style>\r\n.video-wrapper {\r\n  position: relative;\r\n  width: 100%;\r\n  max-width: 560px;   /* optional */\r\n  aspect-ratio: 16 / 9;\r\n}\r\n\r\n.video-wrapper iframe {\r\n  width: 100%;\r\n  height: 100%;\r\n  border: 0;\r\n}\r\n</style>',1,'2026-02-25 16:01:04','2026-02-25 16:01:04');
