strong> stands out due to its diverse services, creative approach, and integrated travel solutions.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><!-- /wp:paragraph --><!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} --></p>\r\n\r\n<h3>🌟 Our Event Management Services</h3>\r\n\r\n<p><!-- /wp:heading --><!-- wp:paragraph --></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Clients trust us for a wide range of events, including:</p>\r\n\r\n<p><!-- /wp:paragraph --><!-- wp:paragraph --></p>\r\n\r\n<p>✅ <strong>Corporate Events</strong> &ndash; Conferences, product launches, and networking sessions. ✅ <strong>Luxury &amp; VIP Events</strong> &ndash; Yacht parties, exclusive gatherings, and high-end experiences. ✅ <strong>Gala Dinners &amp; Award Ceremonies</strong> &ndash; Elegant, theme-based celebrations. ✅ <strong>Festivals &amp; Concerts</strong> &ndash; Large-scale event production and artist bookings. ✅ <strong>Destination Events</strong> &ndash; International retreats and corporate getaways in Lebanon.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><!-- /wp:paragraph --><!-- wp:heading --></p>\r\n\r\n<h2>🌍 How We Compare to Other Event Planners</h2>\r\n\r\n<p><!-- /wp:heading --><!-- wp:table --></p>\r\n\r\n<table>\r\n	<tbody>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td><strong>Feature</strong></td>\r\n			<td><strong>World Wide Travel &amp; Tourism</strong></td>\r\n			<td><strong><a href=\"https://specialeventsleb.com/\">Competitor A</a></strong></td>\r\n			<td><strong>Competitor B</strong></td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td><strong>Corporate &amp; Private Events</strong></td>\r\n			<td>✅</td>\r\n			<td>✅</td>\r\n			<td>✅</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td><strong>Destination Event Planning</strong></td>\r\n			<td>✅</td>\r\n			<td>❌</td>\r\n			<td>✅</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td><strong>Luxury &amp; VIP Event Services</strong></td>\r\n			<td>✅</td>\r\n			<td>✅</td>\r\n			<td>❌</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td><strong>Full Travel &amp; Hospitality Support</strong></td>\r\n			<td>✅</td>\r\n			<td>❌</td>\r\n			<td>❌</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td><strong>Custom Theme &amp; D&eacute;cor</strong></td>\r\n			<td>✅</td>\r\n			<td>✅</td>\r\n			<td>✅</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td><strong>24/7 Event Support</strong></td>\r\n			<td>✅</td>\r\n			<td>✅</td>\r\n			<td>❌</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n	</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n\r\n<p><!-- /wp:table --><!-- wp:paragraph --></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Unlike many competitors, <strong>World Wide Travel &amp; Tourism</strong> provides a fully integrated service, combining event management with hospitality, travel, and VIP concierge solutions.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><!-- /wp:paragraph --><!-- wp:heading --></p>\r\n\r\n<h2>📝 How to Choose the Best Event Management Company in Lebanon</h2>\r\n\r\n<p><!-- /wp:heading --><!-- wp:paragraph --></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Selecting the right event planner requires careful consideration. To make an informed decision, take these factors into account:</p>\r\n\r\n<p><!-- /wp:paragraph --><!-- wp:paragraph --></p>\r\n\r\n<p>🔹 <strong>Review Experience &amp; Portfolio</strong> &ndash; A solid track record demonstrates expertise and reliability. 🔹 <strong>Assess Service Offerings</strong> &ndash; Ensure they provide the specific services you need. 🔹 <strong>Check Vendor Networks</strong> &ndash; Strong relationships with top-tier suppliers enhance execution quality. 🔹 <strong>Look for Customization Options</strong> &ndash; Personalized events create unique and unforgettable experiences. 🔹 <strong>Compare Pricing &amp; Flexibility</strong> &ndash; High-quality services should fit within your budget.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><!-- /wp:paragraph --><!-- wp:paragraph --></p>\r\n\r\n<p>A well-researched decision ensures an exceptional event without unnecessary complications.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><!-- /wp:paragraph --><!-- wp:heading --></p>\r\n\r\n<h2>❓ Frequently Asked Questions (FAQ)</h2>\r\n\r\n<p><!-- /wp:heading --><!-- wp:paragraph --></p>\r\n\r\n<p>🔹 <strong>Which event management companies in Lebanon are the best?</strong> Some of the most reputable event planners include <strong>World Wide Travel &amp; Tourism, XYZ Events, ABC Event Planners, Lebanon Party Planners, and Grand Gala Events</strong>.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><!-- /wp:paragraph --><!-- wp:paragraph --></p>\r\n\r\n<p>🔹 <strong>How much does event planning cost in Lebanon?</strong> Pricing varies based on factors such as event size, location, and required services. To receive a customized quote, contact your preferred event planner.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><!-- /wp:paragraph --><!-- wp:paragraph --></p>\r\n\r\n<p>🔹 <strong>How far in advance should I hire an event planner?</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p><!-- /wp:paragraph --><!-- wp:list --></p>\r\n\r\n<ul><!-- wp:list-item -->\r\n	<li><strong>Corporate events</strong> &ndash; Book <strong>3-6 months</strong> ahead.</li>\r\n	<!-- /wp:list-item --><!-- wp:list-item -->\r\n	<li><strong>Large-scale events &amp; weddings</strong> &ndash; Reserve <strong>6-12 months</strong> in advance for top availability.</li>\r\n	<!-- /wp:list-item -->\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><!-- /wp:list --><!-- wp:paragraph --></p>\r\n\r\n<p>🔹 <strong>Do Lebanese event planners work with international clients?</strong> Absolutely! Many companies, including <strong>World Wide Travel &amp; Tourism</strong>, specialize in <strong>destination events</strong>, offering full-service travel, accommodation, and event planning for international clients.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><!-- /wp:paragraph --><!-- wp:heading --></p>\r\n\r\n<h2>📞 Contact Lebanon&rsquo;s Best Event Management Company!</h2>\r\n\r\n<p><!-- /wp:heading --><!-- wp:paragraph --></p>\r\n\r\n<p>🚀 <strong>Bring your vision to life!</strong> Whether you&rsquo;re organizing a corporate gathering, luxury event, or destination celebration, <strong>World Wide Travel &amp; Tourism</strong> ensures a smooth and unforgettable experience.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><!-- /wp:paragraph --><!-- wp:paragraph --></p>\r\n\r\n<p>📞 <strong>Call Now:</strong>+96170275475<br />\r\n🌍 <strong>Explore Our Blog:</strong> <em><a href=\"https://worldwidetravel-lb.com/blog/43/the-best-travel-agency-for-your-next-adventure\">The Best Travel Agency for Your Next Adventure</a></em><br />\r\n📧 <strong>Email Us:</strong> <a href=\"mailto:info@worldwidetravel-lb.com\">&nbsp;info@worldwidetravel-lb.com</a><br />\r\n📍 <strong>Book your event today with Lebanon&rsquo;s most trusted event planners!</strong> 🎉</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"event management companies in lebanon\" src=\"https://worldwidetravel-lb.com/storage/390/conversions/event-35-thumb-medium.jpg\" style=\"height:500px; width:750px\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p><!-- /wp:paragraph --></p>',1,'2025-02-11 07:22:42','2025-03-12 18:47:07'),
(43,'the Best Travel Agency for Your Next Adventure','explore','google.com','2019-03-18',0,NULL,'<p><!-- wp:paragraph --></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Introduction</strong> Planning a trip can be exciting yet overwhelming. Whether you&#39;re traveling for leisure or business, choosing a reliable <strong>travel agency</strong> ensures a seamless experience. If you&#39;re searching for the best <strong>travel agency in Lebanon</strong>, this guide will help you make the right choice.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><!-- /wp:paragraph --><!-- wp:heading --></p>\r\n\r\n<h2><strong>Why Use a Travel Agency?</strong> A <strong>travel agency</strong> takes the stress out of planning by offering:</h2>\r\n\r\n<p><!-- /wp:heading --><!-- wp:list --></p>\r\n\r\n<ul><!-- wp:list-item -->\r\n	<li>Expert advice on destinations and itineraries</li>\r\n	<!-- /wp:list-item --><!-- wp:list-item -->\r\n	<li>Exclusive travel deals and discounts</li>\r\n	<!-- /wp:list-item --><!-- wp:list-item -->\r\n	<li>Hassle-free flight and hotel bookings</li>\r\n	<!-- /wp:list-item --><!-- wp:list-item -->\r\n	<li>Assistance with visas and travel insurance</li>\r\n	<!-- /wp:list-item -->\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><!-- /wp:list --><!-- wp:paragraph --></p>\r\n\r\n<p>For a full list of our services, visit World Wide Travel and Tourism.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><!-- /wp:paragraph --><!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} --></p>\r\n\r\n<h3>The Role of Travel Agencies in Trip Planning</h3>\r\n\r\n<p><!-- /wp:heading --><!-- wp:paragraph --></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Travel agencies act as intermediaries between travelers and service providers. They help:</p>\r\n\r\n<p><!-- /wp:paragraph --><!-- wp:list --></p>\r\n\r\n<ul><!-- wp:list-item -->\r\n	<li>Find the best travel routes and accommodations</li>\r\n	<!-- /wp:list-item --><!-- wp:list-item -->\r\n	<li>Customize travel experiences based on preferences</li>\r\n	<!-- /wp:list-item --><!-- wp:list-item -->\r\n	<li>Handle last-minute changes or emergencies</li>\r\n	<!-- /wp:list-item -->\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><!-- /wp:list --><!-- wp:paragraph --></p>\r\n\r\n<p>To learn more about customized travel solutions, check out our tailor-made packages.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><!-- /wp:paragraph --><!-- wp:paragraph --></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Top Travel Companies in Lebanon</strong> Lebanon is home to several reputable <strong>travel companies</strong> that offer a variety of services. Whether you&rsquo;re in <strong>Beirut</strong> or another city, here are some factors to consider when selecting the right agency:</p>\r\n\r\n<p><!-- /wp:paragraph --><!-- wp:list {\"ordered\":true,\"start\":1} --></p>\r\n\r\n<ol start=\"1\"><!-- wp:list-item -->\r\n	<li><strong>Reputation &amp; Reviews</strong> &ndash; Check customer feedback online.</li>\r\n	<!-- /wp:list-item --><!-- wp:list-item -->\r\n	<li><strong>Services Offered</strong> &ndash; Look for comprehensive travel packages.</li>\r\n	<!-- /wp:list-item --><!-- wp:list-item -->\r\n	<li><strong>Pricing &amp; Deals</strong> &ndash; Compare offers to get the best value.</li>\r\n	<!-- /wp:list-item --><!-- wp:list-item -->\r\n	<li><strong>Customer Support</strong> &ndash; Ensure they provide reliable assistance.</li>\r\n	<!-- /wp:list-item -->\r\n</ol>\r\n\r\n<p><!-- /wp:list --><!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} --></p>\r\n\r\n<h3>Comparing Travel Agencies in Beirut, Lebanon</h3>\r\n\r\n<p><!-- /wp:heading --><!-- wp:paragraph --></p>\r\n\r\n<p>For those located in the capital, there are many <strong>travel agencies in Beirut, Lebanon</strong> that cater to both local and international travelers. They specialize in:</p>\r\n\r\n<p><!-- /wp:paragraph --><!-- wp:list --></p>\r\n\r\n<ul><!-- wp:list-item -->\r\n	<li>Family vacations</li>\r\n	<!-- /wp:list-item --><!-- wp:list-item -->\r\n	<li>Honeymoon packages</li>\r\n	<!-- /wp:list-item --><!-- wp:list-item -->\r\n	<li>Business travel solutions</li>\r\n	<!-- /wp:list-item --><!-- wp:list-item -->\r\n	<li>Group tours</li>\r\n	<!-- /wp:list-item -->\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><!-- /wp:list --><!-- wp:paragraph --></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Find out about our exclusive honeymoon packages for a romantic getaway.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><!-- /wp:paragraph --><!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} --></p>\r\n\r\n<h3><strong>Benefits of Booking with a Travel Agency in Lebanon</strong> Opting for a <strong>travel agency in Lebanon</strong> ensures:</h3>\r\n\r\n<p><!-- /wp:heading --><!-- wp:list --></p>\r\n\r\n<ul><!-- wp:list-item -->\r\n	<li>Local expertise and destination knowledge</li>\r\n	<!-- /wp:list-item --><!-- wp:list-item -->\r\n	<li>Arabic and English-speaking agents for better communication</li>\r\n	<!-- /wp:list-item --><!-- wp:list-item -->\r\n	<li>Special deals on Middle Eastern and international destinations</li>\r\n	<!-- /wp:list-item -->\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><!-- /wp:list --><!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} --></p>\r\n\r\n<h3>How to Choose the Right Travel Agent in Lebanon</h3>\r\n\r\n<p><!-- /wp:heading --><!-- wp:paragraph --></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Finding a reliable <strong>travel agent in Lebanon</strong> is easier when you:</p>\r\n\r\n<p><!-- /wp:paragraph --><!-- wp:list --></p>\r\n\r\n<ul><!-- wp:list-item -->\r\n	<li>Ask for recommendations from friends and family</li>\r\n	<!-- /wp:list-item --><!-- wp:list-item -->\r\n	<li>Visit agency websites to compare packages</li>\r\n	<!-- /wp:list-item --><!-- wp:list-item -->\r\n	<li>Check if the agency is accredited and licensed</li>\r\n	<!-- /wp:list-item -->\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><!-- /wp:list --><!-- wp:paragraph --></p>\r\n\r\n<p>For a trusted and reputable travel partner, visit our about us page.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><!-- /wp:paragraph --><!-- wp:paragraph --></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Conclusion</strong> Choosing the right travel agency can make all the difference in your travel experience. Whether you&#39;re looking for a <strong>travel agency in Beirut</strong> or elsewhere in Lebanon, doing your research will ensure a smooth and enjoyable trip. Moreover, travel agencies help navigate unforeseen challenges, making your trip stress-free. Ready to start your adventure? Contact a trusted <strong>travel agency</strong> today!</p>\r\n\r\n<p><!-- /wp:paragraph --><!-- wp:paragraph --></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>FAQs</strong> <em>Q: What are the best travel companies in Lebanon?</em> A: The best companies offer great packages, excellent customer service, and competitive pricing. Look for agencies with positive reviews.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><!-- /wp:paragraph --><!-- wp:paragraph --></p>\r\n\r\n<p><em>Q: How much do travel agencies charge for booking?</em> A: Fees vary by agency. Some earn commissions from airlines and hotels, while others charge service fees.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><!-- /wp:paragraph --><!-- wp:paragraph --></p>\r\n\r\n<p><em>Q: Can I get discounts by booking through a travel agency?</em> A: Yes! Many <strong>travel agencies in Lebanon</strong> have exclusive deals not available online.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><!-- /wp:paragraph --><!-- wp:paragraph --></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Worried About Travel Scams?</strong><br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Many travelers in Lebanon are falling victim to fake booking websites and unverified agencies. We&rsquo;ve published a</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>step-by-step guide on how to<a href=\"https://worldwidetravel-lb.com/blog/43/the-best-travel-agency-for-your-next-adventure\"> travel safely in 2025</a></strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>&mdash; don&rsquo;t book without reading it first.</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\" travel agency\" src=\"https://b-gate.org/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/DALL·E-2025-02-18-15.46.26-A-vibrant-and-eye-catching-travel-themed-image-featuring-a-traveler-with-a-suitcase-standing-at-an-airport-looking-at-a-digital-departure-board.-The-.webp\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p><!-- /wp:paragraph --><!-- wp:paragraph --></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><!-- /wp:paragraph --></p>',0,'2025-02-18 11:54:52','2025-07-22 06:50:33'),
(44,'Top Event Management Companies in Lebanon: Making Events Simple and Special','Event Planning & Management',NULL,'2025-04-02',0,NULL,'<p><strong>Planning an event takes time, creativity, and good organization. Event management companies</strong> help bring ideas to life for corporate meetings, weddings, and festivals. Lebanon is known for its lively culture and great hospitality. Many agencies offer event planning services, catering to different needs, from small private celebrations to large corporate conferences. If you&#39;re looking for the <strong>top event management companies in Lebanon</strong>, this guide will help you find the right one.</p>\r\n\r\n<h2>Why Hire an Event Management Company?</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Professional <strong>event management companies</strong> make event planning easy. Here&rsquo;s why hiring one is a good idea:</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><strong>Smooth Planning &amp; Organization</strong>: They take care of all details, from securing venues to coordinating logistics and vendors.</li>\r\n	<li><strong>Creative Event Ideas</strong>: They design unique and engaging events that match your vision, whether it&rsquo;s an elegant wedding or a high-energy product launch.</li>\r\n	<li><strong>Save Time &amp; Money</strong>: They help avoid extra costs, negotiate better deals, and prevent last-minute surprises.</li>\r\n	<li><strong>Stress-Free Execution</strong>: They handle everything on event day, allowing you to focus on your guests and enjoy the occasion.</li>\r\n	<li><strong>Expert Networking</strong>: With established connections in the industry, they can secure top-notch services such as catering, entertainment, and decorations at the best rates.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<h2>Top Event Management Companies in Lebanon</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Lebanon has many trusted event planners. Here are some of the <strong>top event management companies in Lebanon</strong> that consistently deliver outstanding results:</p>\r\n\r\n<h3>1. <strong>World Wide Travel and Tourism</strong></h3>\r\n\r\n<p>This company specializes in corporate events, concerts, and private gatherings. They have a strong reputation for delivering high-quality productions with professional execution.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3>2. <strong>Senses Events</strong></h3>\r\n\r\n<p>Known for its innovative approach, Senses Events excels in wedding planning, brand activations, and luxury events, bringing elegance and creativity to every occasion.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3>3. <strong>Rita Nammour Events</strong></h3>\r\n\r\n<p>Rita Nammour Events focuses on planning tailor-made weddings and corporate events, ensuring a seamless and personalized experience for clients.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3>4. <strong>Level 5 Events</strong></h3>\r\n\r\n<p>With years of experience, Level 5 Events is a go-to choice for large-scale events, including conferences, exhibitions, and public gatherings.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3>5. <strong>Orient Events</strong></h3>\r\n\r\n<p>Orient Events is known for its meticulous attention to detail, managing everything from private celebrations to high-profile corporate events with precision and style.</p>\r\n\r\n<h2>How to Choose the Right Event Planner</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>When selecting an event company, consider these factors:</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><strong>Experience &amp; Past Events</strong>: Review their portfolio to see their previous work and ensure they match your expectations.</li>\r\n	<li><strong>Customer Reviews &amp; Testimonials</strong>: Positive feedback from past clients is a strong indicator of reliability and service quality.</li>\r\n	<li><strong>Services Provided</strong>: Ensure they offer the specific services you need, such as stage setup, lighting, entertainment, or catering.</li>\r\n	<li><strong>Budget-Friendly Options</strong>: Compare pricing to find a company that delivers quality within your budget.</li>\r\n	<li><strong>Flexibility &amp; Customization</strong>: A good event planner should be able to tailor their services to meet your unique requirements.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<h2>Additional Services Offered by Event Management Companies</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Beyond planning, many <strong>event management companies</strong> in Lebanon offer extra services to enhance your event experience:</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><strong>Destination Event Planning</strong>: If you&rsquo;re hosting an event outside your city, they manage all travel and accommodation arrangements.</li>\r\n	<li><strong>Event Branding &amp; Marketing</strong>: For business events, planners can create promotional materials, social media campaigns, and press releases.</li>\r\n	<li><strong>Audiovisual &amp; Production Services</strong>: High-quality sound, lighting, and stage design can transform an event into a spectacular experience.</li>\r\n	<li><strong>Post-Event Services</strong>: Some companies offer follow-ups, feedback collection, and media coverage to ensure your event leaves a lasting impact.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<h2>Conclusion</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Hiring the best <strong>event management companies</strong> in Lebanon ensures a smooth and successful event. Whether it&rsquo;s a corporate event, wedding, festival, or brand activation, the <strong>top event management companies in Lebanon</strong> bring creativity, professionalism, and expertise to every occasion. Let World Wide Travel and Tourism help you find the perfect event planner to turn your vision into reality!</p>\r\n\r\n<p>For expert travel and event planning, visit <a href=\"https://www.worldwidetravel-lb.com/blog/35/top-event-management-companies-in-lebanon-your-guide-to-creating-unforgettable-events\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>World Wide Travel and Tourism</strong></a> today!</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>',1,'2025-04-02 06:35:20','2025-04-02 06:52:14'),
(45,'Report shows airlines making slow progress with NDC technology','reports',NULL,'2025-04-03',0,NULL,'<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:18.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\">While two-thirds of airlines have at least begun the process of&nbsp;</span></span><a href=\"https://www.travelweekly.com/Podcasts/Folo/Airline-NDC-strategies\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"using NDC technology\"><span style=\"font-size:18.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\"><span style=\"color:black\">using NDC technology</span></span></span></a><span style=\"font-size:18.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\">&nbsp;to digitize their third-party merchandising capabilities, only 27% have begun the holistic approach of digitizing their order processing, servicing and settlement capabilities.&nbsp;</span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\">That&#39;s according to a new study from Atmosphere Research Group.&nbsp;</span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\">&quot;There is progress,&quot; Atmosphere founder Henry Harteveldt said in an interview. &quot;And as I say in the report, the only thing that moves fast at an airline are the airplanes.&quot;&nbsp;</span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\">Atmosphere surveyed 78 airlines online and conducted phone interviews with 28 retailing professionals for its &quot;Future of Airline Retailing&quot; report. The study was supported by Accelya, a leader in developing digital merchandising and order-management solutions for airlines.</span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\">Proponents of modernizing airline retailing aspire for the industry to sell airline products and service orders via digital platforms that have similar capabilities to online retailers like Amazon. On the sales side, that means using a wide selection of product images. It also means personalizing search query responses through the effective use of a customer&#39;s previous purchase history as well as other customer metrics.</span></span></span></span></p>',1,'2025-04-03 04:43:10','2025-04-03 04:43:10'),
(47,'United Adds More Offbeat Destinations: Bangkok, Ho Chi Minh City and Adelaide',NULL,NULL,'2025-04-03',0,NULL,'<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"background-color:white\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:18.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\"><span style=\"color:black\">Skift Take</span></span></span></strong></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"background-color:white\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\"><span style=\"color:black\">The latest expansion is a part of United&rsquo;s strategy to bet on off-the-beaten path international destinations.</span></span></span></strong></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"background-color:white\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\"><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\">United Airlines is expanding its West Coast network with a slate of new destinations to Asia and Australia.&nbsp;</span></span></span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"background-color:white\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\"><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\">The carrier announced Wednesday that it will operate daily flights to Bangkok and Ho Chi Minh City from Hong Kong. The routes will connect through Hong Kong from Los Angeles and San Francisco, said United executive Patrick</span></span></span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\">These new services come as part of a broader strategy by United to tap into international markets that are less saturated and offer more niche opportunities for growth. In addition to the daily flights to Thailand and Vietnam, United is also adding a service to Adelaide, Australia, which will further enhance its position in the Pacific region.</span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\">&ldquo;We&#39;re seeing strong demand from travelers seeking unique, off-the-beaten-path experiences, and we believe these new destinations will provide just that,&rdquo; Quayle added. United&rsquo;s decision to focus on cities like Bangkok, Ho Chi Minh City, and Adelaide reflects a growing trend toward catering to travelers looking for alternatives to the most popular international hubs.</span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\">The airline&rsquo;s expansion into these less-traveled cities is likely to appeal to both business and leisure travelers, especially as the demand for long-haul, diverse itineraries continues to rise. By connecting these cities with major hubs like Los Angeles and San Francisco, United is not only increasing accessibility to new markets but also improving its competitive edge in the Asia-Pacific region.</span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\">United&rsquo;s move is also seen as a response to the increasing competition in the international travel space, with airlines around the world seeking to capitalize on emerging destinations.</span></span></span></span></p>',1,'2025-04-03 05:04:10','2025-04-03 05:04:10'),
(48,'What is Driving Trip Decisions of Indian Travelers',NULL,NULL,'2025-04-03',0,NULL,'<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\">For 50% of Indian travelers, travel influencers are a key source of inspiration for deciding their next destination, a report by travel technology company Amadeus has revealed. This figure is nearly double that of the U.S., and significantly higher than other countries such as the UK, Germany, and France, Amadeus said.</span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\">The report noted that the channels driving travel have shifted, with social media ads and travel influencers rising the most in influence over the last five years. Meanwhile, legacy promotion channels such as newspapers, in-person travel agents, and TV ads have been witnessing a fluctuation in importance.</span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\">Earlier this year, online travel company Agoda had also said that Instagram has become the biggest source of travel inspiration for Indian Gen Z travelers. Beyond social media, digital platforms such as Google searches, travel blogs or vlogs, and travel apps are the go-to for the travelers in this generation. These sources are replacing recommendations from friends and family, Agoda had noted.</span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\">In its report, Amadeus also found these trends:</span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\">Hotel guests in India are willing to pay extra for more features. Amadeus noted that on average, Indian travelers are willing to pay 16% above the standard average daily rate to get the view they want. &ldquo;The research shows these features could add around 12% to the average daily rate (ADR) charged by the hotel,&rdquo; it said.</span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\">Additionally, Indian travelers are also prioritizing personalized experiences, with a growing demand for tailor-made travel packages and bespoke services. Many are opting for experiences that offer unique cultural encounters, adventure activities, or wellness retreats. This shift reflects an evolving travel mindset that values authenticity and personalization, particularly among the younger generation.</span></span></span></span></p>',1,'2025-04-03 05:06:28','2025-04-03 05:06:28'),
(49,'Princess Cruises Cancels 2026-27 Sailings From Galveston',NULL,NULL,'2025-04-03',0,NULL,'<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:18.0pt\">Citing its &ldquo;broader global fleet deployment strategy,&rdquo; Princess Cruises has canceled five months of cruises that were slated to set sail from Galveston starting next year.</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:18.0pt\">The company cancelled all scheduled trips on Majestic Princess that were scheduled to depart from Galveston between November 2026 and March 2027, reports the Houston Chronicle.</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:18.0pt\">The company is offering full refunds to affected customers or suggesting alternative cruises.</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:18.0pt\">Regal Princess, meanwhile, will continue to sail all scheduled cruises through and including March 15, 2026, reports USA Today.</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:18.0pt\">&ldquo;We sincerely regret any inconvenience this may cause our guests and appreciate their understanding as we work to enhance our global cruise offerings,&rdquo; according to a statement from the company</span>.</span></span></p>',1,'2025-04-03 05:08:35','2025-04-03 05:08:35'),
(50,'Recognizing Sustainability Leaders Driving the Forward Faster Initiative',NULL,NULL,'2025-04-15',0,NULL,'<p>On Thursday, April 10, <strong>World Wide Travel and Tourism</strong> proudly participated in the <strong>UN Global Compact Network Lebanon&rsquo;s Annual General Assembly</strong>, an important event dedicated to promoting sustainable business practices across Lebanon.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>During the event, industry leaders, partners, and stakeholders gathered to highlight key achievements and future goals in advancing sustainability and responsible business. A major highlight of the assembly was the recognition of companies committed to the <strong>Forward Faster initiative</strong>&mdash;a global UN Global Compact campaign that drives private sector efforts toward achieving the <strong>Sustainable Development Goals (SDGs) by 2030</strong>.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>We are honored to announce that <strong>World Wide Travel and Tourism was officially recognized as one of the first travel companies in Lebanon</strong> to join the <strong>Forward Faster initiative</strong>. This achievement showcases our dedication to creating <strong>sustainable tourism experiences</strong> and strengthening our role as a <strong>sustainable travel agency in Lebanon</strong>.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Our mission goes beyond providing exceptional travel services&mdash;we are committed to promoting <strong>eco-friendly travel solutions</strong>, supporting <strong>sustainable development</strong>, and making a meaningful impact in Lebanon&rsquo;s tourism sector.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>As we move forward, we will continue to innovate, grow, and lead by example in sustainable tourism, while offering our clients unforgettable travel experiences that respect the planet and support local communities.</p>',1,'2025-04-15 04:47:48','2025-04-15 05:05:38'),
