(1,'Project Management','<p><strong>Budgeting</strong>: Transparent financial planning, expense tracking, and reporting<br />\r\n<strong>Hotel </strong>Accommodation: Room reservations, group rates, hospitality suites, and VIP services<br />\r\n<strong>Transportation</strong>: Airport and internal transfers, car rentals, taxis, trains, and tour buses<br />\r\n<strong>Venue Hire</strong>: Selection and reservation of conference rooms, halls, and outdoor spaces<br />\r\n<strong>Travel Solutions:</strong> Ticketing, corporate travel management, visas, and insurance plans</p>',1,'https://youtu.be/Ty64Bdhc55E','https://youtu.be/Ty64Bdhc55E',1,'2023-01-24 11:35:53','2025-08-20 17:48:31');
