(47,'Sri Lanka Package from Lebanon','Sri Lanka','1.222','9 Days / 8 Nights',0,NULL,'Sri Lanka-Package-from-Lebanon-–-9-Days-/-8-Nights-(Sept 23–Oct 1)-6M2841496604317','<h1>Sri&nbsp;Lanka Package &ndash; 9 Days / 8 Nights (Sept&nbsp;23&ndash;Oct&nbsp;1)</h1>\r\n\r\n<p>Embark on a spectacular <strong>Sri&nbsp;Lanka tour from Lebanon</strong> this autumn. Our 9‑day, 8‑night adventure (Sept&nbsp;23 &ndash; Oct&nbsp;1) includes roundtrip flights, premium hotels, private transfers with an English/Arabic chauffeur‑guide and a ready visa for your convenience. Explore Colombo&rsquo;s vibrant streets, marvel at the Dambulla cave temples, feel the cultural heartbeat of Kandy and unwind on Beruwala&rsquo;s golden beaches &mdash; all at a competitive starting price of <strong>$1,222 per person</strong>.</p>\r\n\r\n<h2>What&rsquo;s Included</h2>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><strong>Roundtrip flights</strong> with Air Arabia from Beirut to Sri&nbsp;Lanka</li>\r\n	<li><strong>4★ &amp; 5★ hotels</strong> with Half Board/Full Board meals</li>\r\n	<li><strong>Private transfers</strong> with English/Arabic chauffeur‑guide</li>\r\n	<li><strong>Visa</strong> arranged for hassle‑free entry</li>\r\n	<li><strong>5GB e‑SIM</strong> for connectivity</li>\r\n	<li>All taxes, tolls and government fees</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<h2>Itinerary Highlights</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Discover Colombo&rsquo;s colonial architecture and bustling markets. Journey to the ancient Dambulla caves and experience the cultural heart of Kandy, home to the Temple of the Sacred Tooth Relic. End your trip relaxing on Beruwala&rsquo;s famed beaches, where calm waters meet golden sand.</p>\r\n\r\n<h2>Limited Spots &ndash; Book Now</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>This Sri&nbsp;Lanka package has a limited number of seats. <a href=\"{{ url(\'/contact\') }}\">Contact our Beirut office</a> today or explore related offers like our <a href=\"{{ url(\'/package/honeymoon-sri-lanka\') }}\">Honeymoon Sri&nbsp;Lanka</a> package or <a href=\"{{ url(\'/package/maldives\')