(54,'Zanzibar & Tanzania Safari Package from Lebanon | 7 Days of Adventure','Tanzania, United Republic of',NULL,'7 Days',0,NULL,'Zanzibar-&-Tanzania-Safari-Package-from-Lebanon-|-7-Days-of-Adventure-3812376120T1459','<h1>Into Zanzibar&rsquo;s Wild &amp; Serene Wonders: The Ultimate Lebanese Escape 🇹🇿</h1>\r\n\r\n<h2>7 Days of Bush &amp; Beach: Your All-Inclusive Itinerary</h2>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>\r\n	<p>Ditch the routine and immerse yourself in the golden plains of Tanzania and the turquoise waters of Zanzibar. This curated 7-day journey is designed specifically for the Lebanese traveler who seeks a perfect blend of high-octane adventure and total island serenity.</p>\r\n\r\n	<p><strong>Why Book This Package?</strong></p>\r\n\r\n	<ul>\r\n		<li>\r\n		<p><strong>Private Safari Excellence:</strong> Unlike group tours, we provide a <strong>Private 4x4 Land Cruiser</strong> and an expert English-speaking guide for your game drives in Selous.</p>\r\n		</li>\r\n		<li>\r\n		<p><strong>Seamless Travel:</strong> Roundtrip flights via <strong>Fly Dubai</strong> with coordinated private transfers.</p>\r\n		</li>\r\n		<li>\r\n		<p><strong>Total Peace of Mind:</strong> Includes comprehensive travel insurance and expert assistance with your <strong>Zanzibar/Tanzania Visa on Arrival</strong>.&nbsp;</p>\r\n		</li>\r\n	</ul>\r\n	</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Q: Do Lebanese citizens need a visa for Zanzibar/Tanzania in 2026?</strong> <strong>A:</strong> Yes, Lebanese passport holders require a visa. You can obtain a <strong>Single Entry Tourist Visa ($50)</strong> either online (E-Visa) or upon arrival at Zanzibar (ZNZ) or Dar es Salaam (DAR) airports. <strong>WWTT provides full documentation support</strong> to ensure a smooth entry. <em>Note: A mandatory Zanzibar Inbound Insurance ($44) is now required for all visitors.</em></p>',0,1,1,'2026-02-25 16:27:14','2026-02-25 16:27:14'),
(55,'Muscat Oman Luxury Escape from Beirut | 5 Days Starting $620 | WWTT','Oman','$620',NULL,0,NULL,'Muscat-Oman-Luxury-Escape-from-Beirut-|-5-Days-Starting-$620-|-WWTT-48374536637390I','<h1>Muscat: A Journey of Soft Golden Light &amp; Refined Omani Charm 🇴🇲</h1>\r\n\r\n<h2>The Perfect 5-Day Balance of Relaxation and Culture</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Experience the serene beauty of the Sultanate. From the architectural marvel of the <strong>Grand Mosque</strong> to the breathtaking scenic coastlines of the Gulf of Oman, our Muscat package is curated for the Lebanese traveler who appreciates refined heritage and calm shores.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Why This Is the Best Value in Lebanon:</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>\r\n	<p><strong>Premium Aviation:</strong> Fly in comfort with <strong>Qatar Airways</strong> (Roundtrip from Beirut).</p>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n	<p><strong>Elite Logistics:</strong> Forget group buses. Enjoy <strong>Private Airport Transfers</strong> for a dignified arrival.</p>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n	<p><strong>Unbeatable Starting Price:</strong> Luxury experiences starting at just <strong>$620 per person</strong>.</p>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n	<p><strong>Peace of Mind:</strong> Full travel insurance included as standard.</p>\r\n	</li>\r\n</ul>',0,1,1,'2026-02-25 16:30:35','2026-02-25 16:30:35'),
(56,'Phu Quoc Vietnam Package from Lebanon | Visa-Free Tropical Escape','Viet Nam',NULL,'5 DAys',0,NULL,'Phu-Quoc-Vietnam-Package-from-Lebanon-|-Visa-Free-Tropical-Escape-G31753783800811','<h1>Phu Quoc Awaits You: 5 Days of Tropical Bliss (No Visa Required!) 🇻🇳✨</h1>\r\n\r\n<h2>The Ultimate Hassle-Free Getaway for Lebanese Travelers</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Leave the paperwork behind and step into paradise. Discover the hidden coral gardens, white-sand shores, and vibrant night markets of Vietnam&rsquo;s premier island destination. Designed for ultimate relaxation, this 5-day journey lets you swim, unwind, and savor fresh seafood by the sea without a single worry.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>𝗔𝗻𝗱 𝘁𝗵𝗲 𝗯𝗲𝘀𝘁 𝗽𝗮𝗿𝘁? 𝗡𝗼 𝘃𝗶𝘀𝗮 𝗶𝘀 𝗻𝗲𝗲𝗱𝗲𝗱 𝗳𝗼𝗿 𝗟𝗲𝗯𝗮𝗻𝗲𝘀𝗲 𝗰𝗶𝘁𝗶𝘇𝗲𝗻𝘀!</strong> Just pack your bags and let us handle the rest.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Your Premium Inclusions:</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>\r\n	<p><strong>World-Class Flights:</strong> Roundtrip tickets with <strong>Turkish Airlines</strong> from Beirut.</p>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n	<p><strong>Island Logistics:</strong> Seamless <strong>Private Airport Transfers</strong> directly to your resort.</p>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n	<p><strong>Comfort:</strong> 4 Nights of handpicked Hotel Accommodation.</p>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n	<p><strong>Security:</strong> Comprehensive Travel Insurance included.&nbsp;</p>\r\n	</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Q: Can Lebanese citizens travel to Phu Quoc, Vietnam without a visa?</strong> <strong>A:</strong> Yes! Under a special exemption policy, <strong>Lebanese citizens do not need a visa</strong> to visit Phu Quoc Island for up to 30 days. As long as you fly directly into Phu Quoc International Airport (or transit internationally without entering mainland Vietnam), you can enjoy a completely visa-free tropical vacation. WWTT handles all flight routings to ensure your visa-free status is protected.</p>',0,1,1,'2026-02-25 16:40:13','2026-02-25 16:40:13');
